Primary Format: JPEG
Dimensions: 1920x1080px (desktop version)
Additional Responsive Versions Required:
- Tablet: 1024x768px
- Mobile: 640x960px

Image Optimization Requirements:
1. JPEG Quality: 80%
2. WebP Version: 75% quality
3. File naming: Include content hash for versioning
4. Compression: Optimized for web delivery while maintaining visual quality

The image should be:
- Used as a full-screen cover background
- Support both light and dark theme modes
- Maintain minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio with overlaid content
- Implement responsive behavior across devices
- Follow WCAG 2.1 Level AA accessibility guidelines

Performance Optimizations:
- Enable eager loading for above-fold visibility
- Implement responsive image loading using srcset
- Configure proper caching headers:
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
- Include ETag for caching optimization

CSS Integration:
- Apply classes: bg-auth-pattern, bg-cover, bg-center, bg-no-repeat
- Support transition-opacity with 300ms duration
- Configure in Tailwind theme under backgroundImage

Accessibility:
- Treat as decorative background (no alt text required)
- Support reduced motion preferences
- Ensure proper contrast ratios in both themes